Main pronunciation 主要发音: zūn

Other pronunciations 其它发音: Not exists.

Original meaning 本义: Meaning to respect.

English senses 英语理解: respect, revere, venerate; honor

Usage example 用法举例: 尊貴 zūn guì (honourable)

Importance by frequency 常用频率: 1013

Shuowen 说文解字: 或從寸臣鉉等曰今俗以尊作尊卑之尊別作罇非是

Decomposition notes 字形分解说明 [?]:
